ng narrative provides a crucial missing piece in the study of the West's attempts to colonize the Middle East during the Middle Ages.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 0aMilitary history, Medieval. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300241143423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300241143.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles